Entries.default: "Things have been getting better around here. By Eothas' will."
"Maren! I'll never hear the end of it from her. And I thank you sincerely for that. I can't wait to hear her voice."
"I feel sick to my stomach, and I'm cold, but given that both those things require being alive? I'm perfectly all right."
The tension in the air draws taut. For a moment the only sounds are the creak of armor, and the crackling of the nearby torch.
